3. cargo - Rustâ€™s build system and package manager
4. cargo new project_name - To create new rust application with package manager
5. cargo build - To build rust project, which build and saves the binary in target/debug/project_name
6. cargo run - To build and run the application
7. cargo build --release - For production level build will be availabel in target/release/project_name
